item.title: 翻转二叉树
item.author: vllbc
item.description: 翻转二叉树 开始学习二叉树了 先来个简单题 https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/invert-binary-tree/ 很简单 # Definition for a binary tree node. # class TreeNode: # def __init__(self, x): # self.val = x # self.left = None # self.right = None class Solution: def invertTree(self, root: TreeNode) -> TreeNode: if root == None: return None temp = root.left root.left = root.right root.right
